This Technology License Agreement (the “
Terms
”) is entered into on the Effective Date by and between the Outbrain entity and Partner identified in the Order Form. Outbrain and Partner may collectively be referred to herein as the Parties and each individually as a Party. These Terms shall apply to any and all agreements between the parties and their Affiliates from time to time.
1.
DEFINITIONS
1.1. “
Content
” means graphical, textual, and/or auditory content (which may include text, data, information, photos, images, graphics, audio, video or other content).
